'''鄧肯·斯科特'''（{{lang-en|Duncan Scott}}；{{bd|1997年|5月6日}}）是一名[[英國|英國]]游泳運動員。他在[[2015年歐洲運動會|2015年歐洲運動會]]上獲得了三枚金牌<ref name="baku">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/swimming/33614260 |title=World Championships: Duncan Scott tipped to add to medal haul |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=21 July 2015 |accessdate=8 August 2015 |archive-date=2019-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614011212/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/swimming/33614260 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成為這屆歐洲運動會上獲得金牌數最多的英國運動員。他也代表英國參加了[[2015年世界游泳錦標賽|2015年世界游泳錦標賽]]<ref name="kazan">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/swimming/33827249 |title=World Swimming Championships: Britain win 4x200m relay gold |publisher=BBC |date=7 August 2015 |accessdate=8 August 2015 |archive-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002003328/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/swimming/33827249 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

斯科特在[[2019年世界游泳锦标赛|2019年世界游泳锦标赛]]上获得男子200米自由泳的并列季军。颁奖典礼期间，与澳籍友人[[麥克·霍爾頓|麥克·霍爾頓]]一样，他拒绝和[[孙杨|孙杨]]握手及与其合影，被认为是表达对前一年发生的孙杨干预[[兴奋剂|兴奋剂]]检测事件及[[国际游泳联合会|国际游泳联合会]]对此事处理的不满。孙杨不满其行为，退场时对其做手势回击，並用英語說“You loser, I am a winner. Yeah!（你这个失败者，我是赢家，耶！）”。后来两人都受到[[国际游泳联合会|国际游泳联合会]]的警告<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/jul/23/adam-peaty-backs-duncan-scott-decision-snub-sun-yang-swimming-world-championships |title='I don't know why he's here': Adam Peaty backs Scott's decision to snub Sun Yang |agency=Reuters |date=2019-07-23 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811043853/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/jul/23/adam-peaty-backs-duncan-scott-decision-snub-sun-yang-swimming-world-championships |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/swimming/2019/07/23/duncan-scott-sent-death-threats-refusing-stand-podium-alongside/ |title=Duncan Scott sent death threats after refusing to shake hands with 'drug cheat' Sun Yang |first=Daniel |last=Schofield |date=2019-07-23 |work=The Telegraph |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archive-date=2019-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723181148/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/swimming/2019/07/23/duncan-scott-sent-death-threats-refusing-stand-podium-alongside/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://sports.sina.com.cn/others/swim/2019-07-23/doc-ihytcerm5756349.shtml |title=孙杨英文霸气回应斯科特：你是失败者 我是赢家！ |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archive-date=2019-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724035121/https://sports.sina.com.cn/others/swim/2019-07-23/doc-ihytcerm5756349.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

